CLUAIDO - Play a detective game with AI characters.

Who Killed Mr. Hamilton?

You were called to the victims' house to solve his misterious death. Talk to the people inside and unveil the clues that will lead you to the culprit.

Game Rules

  • There are 7 suspects and only one culprit inside the house.
  • You can ask whatever you want to the characters.
  • All characters will tell you the truth except for the culprit.
  • You can make 20 questions before the culprit runs away.
  • Clues are concieled within the characters and all over the house.
  • You have only one shot to indentify the culprit.

In order to play this game you will need an account with Gamer Tool Studio and to connect with your API key.
